{"title_page": "Second Crusade", "text_new": "{{Use dmy dates|date=October 2019}}\n{{short description|12th-century crusade, the second major crusade}}\n{{Infobox military conflict\n| conflict = Second Crusade\n| partof = the [[Crusades]]\n| image = BattleOfInab.jpg\n| caption = ''Passage Outremer'' by [[Jean'sColombe]] and [[S\u00e9bastien Momerot]] depicting of the [[Battle of Inab]]\n| date = 1147\u20131150\n| place = [[Iberian Peninsula|Iberia]], [[Near East]] ([[Anatolia]], [[Levant]]), [[Lower Egypt|Egypt]]\n| territory = * [[Lisbon]] captured by the Portuguese and [[Tortosa]] captured by the Catalans.\n* [[Wagria]] and [[Polabia]] captured by the Saxon Crusaders.\n| result = {{Collapsible list|title='''Anatolia:'''|titlestyle=font-weight:normal;background:transparent;text-align:left;|\n* Decisive Turkish victory \n**Crusader failure to restore the [[County of Edessa]]\n**Peace treaty between the Byzantine Empire and the Sultanate of Rum\n**Beginning of [[Crusader invasions of Egypt|Crusader advances into Egypt]]\n}}\n{{Collapsible list|title='''Levant'''|titlestyle=font-weight:normal;background:transparent;text-align:left;|\n* ''[[Status quo ante bellum]]''\n**Zengid military victory \n}}\n{{Collapsible list|title='''Iberia:'''|titlestyle=font-weight:normal;background:transparent;text-align:left;|\n* Decisive Crusader victory\n}}\n| combatant1 = {{Collapsible list|title=[[Crusader States]]|titlestyle=font-weight:normal;background:transparent;text-align:left;|\n* {{Flagicon image|Vexillum Regni Hierosolymae.svg}} [[Kingdom of Jerusalem]]\n* [[County of Tripoli]]\n* [[Principality of Antioch]]\n[[Military order (society)|Military Order]]s\n* {{Flagicon image|Bandeira Templ\u00e1ria.svg}} [[Knights Templar]]\n* {{Flagicon image|Flag of the Order of St. John (various).svg}} [[Knights Hospitaller]]\n* [[Canons Regular of the Holy Sepulchre]]\n* {{Flagicon image|Flag of the Order of Saint Lazarus.svg}} [[Order of Saint Lazarus|Knights of Saint Lazarus]]\n{{flagicon