. They look for them, but no luck. Kevin becomes paranoid and suspicious, and tries to convince everyone it is another nefarious plot by the Eds.\n| LineColor = AEDFED\n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber = 39\n| EpisodeNumber2 = 13\n| Title = Is There an Ed in the House?\n----An Ed is Born\n| DirectedBy = Danny Antonucci\n| WrittenBy = Jono Howard & Danny Antonucci\n----[[Geoff Berner]] & Danny Antonucci\n| Aux2 = Leah Waldron\n----James \"Wootie\" Wootton\n| Aux3 = Is There a Doctor in the House?\n----A Star is Born\n| OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2002|7|12}}\n| ShortSummary = Is There an Ed in the House?: The Eds are \"taking a picture\" of Rolf in their latest scam when they find out that Sarah is sick. Ed and Jimmy both do what they can to take care of her and nurse her back to health, which starts a rivalry between them.\n{{Clear}}An Ed is Born: After Eddy receives baby items from his brother in the mail, he and the other Eds make a home movie to show how mature and popular he is.\n| LineColor = AEDFED\n}}\n}}\n\n===Season 4 (2002\u201304)===\n{{Episode table|overall=|season=|background=#CED31E|title=|director=|writer=|airdate=|airdateR=<ref name=\"iTunes4\">{{cite web|title=Ed, Edd n Eddy, Season 4|url=https://itunes.apple.com/us/tv-season/ed-edd-n-eddy-season-4/id385739972|work=[[iTunes Store]]|publisher=[[Apple Inc.|Apple]]|accessdate=August 25, 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304003436/https://itunes.apple.com/us/tv-season/ed-edd-n-eddy-season-4/id385739972|archive-date=March 4, 2016|url-status=live}}</ref>|aux2=|aux2T=Storyboard by|aux3=|aux3T=Title Reference|episodes=\n\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber = 40\n| EpisodeNumber2 = 1\n| Title = If It Smells Like an Ed\n| DirectedBy = [[Danny Antonucci]]\n| WrittenBy = Geoff Berner, Jono Howard & Danny Antonucci\n| Aux2 = James \"Wootie\" Wootton\n| Aux3 = If It Smells Like a Rat\n| OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2002|9|27}}\n| ShortSummary = When Eddy gives Jimmy a wedgie and humiliates hi