-Look Before You Ed\n| DirectedBy = [[Danny Antonucci]]\n| WrittenBy = Stacy Warnick & Danny Antonucci\n----Stacy Warnick, Rachel Connor & Danny Antonucci\n| Aux2 = Raven Molisee & Sabrina Alberghetti\n----Scott Underwood & Steve Garcia\n| Aux3 = May I Have This Dance?\n----Look Before You Cross/Leap\n| OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2008|6|29}}\n| ShortSummary = May I Have This Ed?: The Peach Creek Jr. High school dance is coming up&nbsp;\u2014 while Eddy is excited about it, Edd is not looking forward to it.\n\n{{Clear}}Look Before You Ed: Edd and Jimmy decide to run a safety club to curb wintertime hazards.\n\n{{Clear}}Note: This episode is in memory of [[Paul Boyd (animator)|Paul Boyd]].\n| LineColor = B8B8B8\n}}\n}}\n\n===Specials {{anchor|Special episodes}}===\n{{Episode table|overall=|season=|background=#000000|title=|director=|writer=|aux2=|aux2T=Storyboard by|aux3=|aux3T=Title Reference|airdate=|episodes=\n\n{{Episode list|\n| EpisodeNumber = 53\n| EpisodeNumber2 = 1\n| Title = Ed, Edd n Eddy's Jingle Jingle Jangle\n| DirectedBy = [[Danny Antonucci]]\n| WrittenBy = [[Jono Howard]], [[Mike Kubat]] & Danny Antonucci\n| Aux2 = \"Big\" Jim Miller, Scott \"Diggs\" Underwood & Leah Waldron\n| Aux3 = Jingle, Jangle, Jingle (Song)\n| OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2004|12|3}}\n| ShortSummary = Disappointed by his gifts at home on [[Christmas Eve]], Eddy decides that if one of the other cul-de-sac children \"adopts\" him, he could get their presents.\n\n| LineColor = 000000\n}}\n{{Episode list|\n| EpisodeNumber = 54\n| EpisodeNumber2 = 2\n| Title = Ed, Edd n Eddy's Hanky Panky Hullabaloo\n| DirectedBy = Danny Antonucci\n| WrittenBy = Jono Howard, Mike Kubat & Danny Antonucci\n| Aux2 = \"Big\" Jim Miller, Scott \"Diggs\" Underwood & Leah Waldron\n| Aux3 = {{TableTBA|none}}\n| OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2005|2|11}}\n| ShortSummary = On Valentine's Day, two cupids are set to fire arrows of love at all the cul-de-sac children at their school, Peach Creek Jr. High.\n